ed="T" n="0797a09"/><persName key="A010882">釋道光</persName><ptr target="#n1067"/>，姓<name>禇</name>氏，<anchor xml:id="beg0797sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>喻</sic><corr>踰</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0797sgsz1"/>齓出家。方冠受具，詣<placeName key="PL000000025908">光<lb
ed="T" n="0797a10"/>州</placeName><ref type="person" target="#A008876">和尚</ref>學通毘尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>。<anchor xml:id="begd1e24198"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e24198"/>時夏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g61"/>淺德崇，壇場屬<lb
ed="T" n="0797a11"/>望，蓋天賚<ptr type="glossary" target="#g425"/>真士，為「東南義虎」，雲雨慈<anchor xml:id="beg0797sgsz2"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>昧</sic><corr>味</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0797sgsz2"/>，笙<lb
ed="T" n="0797a12"/>鏞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g430"/>道聲。<persName key="A010882">光</persName>持《法華經》，創塔廟，洎沒身不怠<lb
ed="T" n="0797a13"/>也。<date from-iso="+0760-09-18" key="j19989051998934" to-iso="+0760-10-17"><name>上元</name>元年庚子仲秋</date>示疾，終<anchor xml:id="begd1e24211"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e24211"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000056835">本寺</ref>，春<lb
ed="T" n="0797a14"/>秋七十九，法臘五十八。是日馳陽昧昧，淫雨<lb
ed="T" n="0797a15"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>㴓㴓</sic><corr>颸颸</corr></choice><ptr target="#n1068"/>，烈風崇朝<ptr type="glossary" target="#g436"/>，嘉木為折，乃東土福盡之徵<lb
ed="T" n="0797a16"/>也。俄然喜氣五色，亭亭如蓋，移晷不散，偏<ptr target="#n1069"/><lb
ed="T" n="0797a17"/>映精<anchor xml:id="beg0797sgsz3"/>廬<anchor xml:id="end0797sgsz3"/>，即西方往生之意也。初<persName key="A010882">光</persName>未歿，<date when-iso="+0760-09-20" key="j19989071998907">其<lb
ed="T" n="0797a18"/>月三日</date>質明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g438"/>，支<ptr target="#n1072"/>疾凝神，依色身觀<ptr target="#n1074"/>，<persName key="A002843">彌陀</persName>具<lb
ed="T" n="0797a19"/>相現在<ref type="person" target="#A010882">其</ref>前。滿庭碧<anchor xml:id="beg0797sgsz4"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0797sgsz4"/>，昔所未覩者。<date when-iso="+0760-09-21" key="j19989081998908">四日</date><lb
ed="T" n="0797a20"/>昧爽<ptr type="glossary" target="#g439"/>，有異人請<persName key="A010882">光</persName>為和尚，遂開目彈指<ptr type="glossary" target="#g507"/>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0797a21"/>「但發菩提心」。至<date when-iso="+0760-09-22" key="j19989091998909">五日</date>，曼陀羅<anchor xml:id="beg0797sgsz5"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0797sgsz5"/>自天而雨。<lb
ed="T" n="0797a22"/>門人<persName key="A019333">神烈</persName>、<persName key="A019334">義津</persName><ptr target="#n1075"/>追慕弗遑，各分法味，流布<lb
ed="T" n="0797a23"/>行化，香火無窮云。</p>
